---
import DefaultLayout from '../../layouts/DefaultLayout.astro';

const pageTitle = 'Medical Record Digitization Case Study | Tyrus Technologies';
const pageDescription =
  'Healthcare document digitization case study for multi-hospital MRD archives, OPD/IPD files, OCR indexing, secure handling, and faster medical record retrieval.';
---

<DefaultLayout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <section class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
      <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-700">Healthcare Case Study</p>
      <h1 class="mt-2 max-w-4xl text-3xl font-semibold text-slate-900">
        Multi-hospital medical record digitization for faster MRD retrieval.
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-3 max-w-3xl text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700">
        Tyrus supports hospitals that need to digitize OPD, IPD, MRD, diagnostic, consent, and
        medico-legal records without disrupting daily admissions or retrieval requests.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50 border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-6xl gap-8 px-4 py-12 md:grid-cols-2">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Project need</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700">
          Hospital record rooms hold years of active and inactive patient files. MRD teams need
          fast retrieval for doctors, insurance, legal cases, audits, and discharge documentation.
          Physical searching can take hours when records are spread across rooms, bundles, or
          offsite storage.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl bg-white p-6 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">Records handled</h3>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-700">
          <li>OPD and IPD case files</li>
          <li>MRD archives and continuation sheets</li>
          <li>Consent forms, discharge summaries, reports, and insurance records</li>
          <li>Legacy cartons and department-wise medical files</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-white border-b border-slate-200">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">How the work was structured</h2>
      <div class="mt-5 grid gap-4 md:grid-cols-4">
        {[
          ['1', 'Survey', 'Record rooms, file types, active retrieval needs, and retention policies were reviewed.'],
          ['2', 'Batching', 'Files were grouped by hospital, year, department, MRN, or episode pattern.'],
          ['3', 'Scanning', 'Sensitive records were scanned with image quality checks and controlled access.'],
          ['4', 'Indexing', 'MRN, patient details, visit type, and department fields supported faster retrieval.']
        ].map(([number, title, text]) => (
          <article class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 p-5 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
            <div class="flex h-9 w-9 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-emerald-600 text-sm font-semibold text-white">{number}</div>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-900">{title}</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-xs leading-6 text-slate-700">{text}</p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-slate-50">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-12">
      <div class="rounded-3xl bg-white p-8 ring-1 ring-slate-200">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-slate-900">Outcome</h2>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-7 text-slate-700">
          Retrieval time dropped significantly because MRD teams could locate records digitally
          instead of searching through physical files. The hospital also reduced pressure on record
          rooms and improved readiness for audit, medico-legal, and insurance requests.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-5 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
          <a href="/medical-record-digitization-services" class="rounded-full bg-emerald-600 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:bg-emerald-700">Medical record digitization</a>
          <a href="/services/medical-record-scanning" class="rounded-full border border-emerald-300 px-5 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-emerald-700 hover:bg-emerald-50">Medical record scanning</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</DefaultLayout>
